[
	{
		"name": "DatePanel.RootProps",
		"kind": "intersection",
		"types": [
			{
				"kind": "interface",
				"properties": [
					{
						"name": "style",
						"summary": "组件根元素的样式\n\n",
						"remarks": "相对于\n，一些简短的样式设置，直接使用此属性更方便，\n还有一些自定义的样式变量也可以使用此属性设置。\n\n",
						"type": "string | JSX.CSSProperties | undefined",
						"reactive": true
					},
					{
						"name": "popover",
						"type": "boolean | \"manual\" | \"auto\" | undefined"
					},
					{
						"name": "class",
						"summary": "为组件的根元素指定 CSS 类名\n\n",
						"remarks": "为当前组件的根元素指定 CSS 类名。该值始终是最后添加到元素的 class 属性上的，\n以保证此类能启作用，当然也有可能会修改组件的定义的一些 CSS 样式。\n\n",
						"type": "string | undefined",
						"reactive": true
					},
					{
						"name": "onChange",
						"summary": "值发生改变时触发的事件\n\n\nval 表示修改的新值；\nold 表示修改之前的值；\ntime 是否只修改了时间部分，该值只有在\n`time`\n为 true 时才有效；\n\n\n此方法只在以下条件下触发：\n- 点击天数；\n- 点击小时、分钟和秒；\n\n",
						"type": "((val?: Date, old?: Date, time?: boolean) => void) | undefined"
					},
					{
						"name": "disabled",
						"summary": "禁用状态\n\n",
						"type": "boolean | undefined",
						"reactive": true
					},
					{
						"name": "palette",
						"summary": "指定当前组件采用的色盘\n\n",
						"remarks": "如果指定了此值，那么在组件内部的 CSS 引用的诸如\n`--palette-bg`\n等 CSS 变量都将使用此色盘对应的颜色。\n如果是 undefined，则表示从父元素继承。\n\n",
						"type": "\"primary\" | \"secondary\" | \"tertiary\" | \"error\" | \"surface\" | undefined",
						"reactive": true
					},
					{
						"name": "value",
						"summary": "关联的值\n\n",
						"type": "Date | undefined"
					},
					{
						"name": "readonly",
						"summary": "只读状态\n\n",
						"type": "boolean | undefined",
						"reactive": true
					},
					{
						"name": "time",
						"summary": "是否符带时间选择器\n\n",
						"type": "boolean | undefined",
						"reactive": true
					},
					{
						"name": "min",
						"summary": "允许的最小日期\n\n",
						"type": "Date | undefined"
					},
					{
						"name": "max",
						"summary": "允许的最大日期\n\n",
						"type": "Date | undefined"
					},
					{
						"name": "weekend",
						"summary": "是否高亮周末的列\n\n",
						"type": "boolean | undefined",
						"reactive": true
					},
					{
						"name": "weekBase",
						"summary": "一周的开始，默认为 0，即周日。\n\n",
						"type": "0 | 5 | 4 | 3 | 2 | 1 | 6 | undefined",
						"reactive": true
					},
					{
						"name": "weeks",
						"summary": "是否显示周数\n\n\nNOTE: 周数是依据 ISO 8601 拿所在行的中间列计算所得。\n如果\n`weekBase`\n不为 1，那么周数指向的可能并不是当前行。\n\n",
						"type": "boolean | undefined",
						"reactive": true
					},
					{
						"name": "onWeekClick",
						"summary": "点击周数时的回调函数\n\n",
						"type": "((week: WeekValueType, range: [Date, Date]) => void) | undefined"
					},
					{
						"name": "onPaging",
						"summary": "翻页时的回调函数\n\n",
						"type": "((val: Date, old?: Date) => void) | undefined"
					},
					{
						"name": "plugins",
						"summary": "插件列表\n\n\nNOTE: 这是一个非响应式的属性。\n\n",
						"type": "DatetimePlugin[] | undefined"
					}
				]
			},
